      "text": "東京に戻ったら、この浴衣を着て\n優とすみれと一緒に出掛けてみたいです",
      "startTime": 310.2000246685,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
